32 SECTION 1.(d) G.S. 88B-12 reads as rewritten:
33 "§ 88B-12. Temporary employment permit; extensions; limits on practice.
34 (a) The Board shall issue a temporary employment permit to an applicant for licensure
35 as an apprentice, cosmetologist, esthetician, natural hair care specialist, or manicurist who meets
