43 from a cosmetic art school and shall not be renewed.
44 (c) The holder of a temporary employment permit may practice cosmetic art only under
45 the supervision of a licensed cosmetologist, manicurist, natural hair care specialist, or esthetician,
46 as appropriate, and may not operate a cosmetic art shop."
